import React from 'react';
import { Card, CardImg, Button, Form, FormGroup, Label, Input, FormText } from 'reactstrap';

const OrderForm = props => {


    return (
        <Form>
            <FormGroup>
                <Label for="name">Name</Label>
                <Input name="name" id="name" placeholder="name" />
            </FormGroup>
            <FormGroup>
        <Label for="exampleSelect">Size</Label>
        <Input type="select" name="select" id="exampleSelect">
          <option>Small</option>
          <option>Medium</option>
          <option>Large</option>
        </Input>
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup check>
        <Label check>
          <Input type="checkbox" id="cheese"/>{' '}
          Cheese
        </Label>
      </FormGroup> 
      <FormGroup check>
        <Label check>
          <Input type="checkbox" id="tomatoes"/>{' '}
          Tomatoes
        </Label>
      </FormGroup> 
      <FormGroup check>
        <Label check>
          <Input type="checkbox" id="blackOlives"/>{' '}
          Black Olives
        </Label>
      </FormGroup> 
      <FormGroup check>
        <Label check>
          <Input type="checkbox" id="lettuce"/>{' '}
          Lettuce
        </Label>
      </FormGroup> 
      <FormGroup check>
        <Label check>
          <Input type="checkbox" id="hotSauce"/>{' '}
          Hot sauce
        </Label>
      </FormGroup> 
      <FormGroup check>
        <Label check>
          <Input type="checkbox" id="sourCream"/>{' '}
           Sour cream
        </Label>
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="exampleText">Special Instructions</Label>
        <Input type="textarea" name="text" id="special" />
      </FormGroup>
      <Button>Submit</Button>
    </Form>
    )
}

export default OrderForm;
